[SN]TITLE[SN]
How much time do you spend on your gadgets each day?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
As part of our new special, 'Is Tech taking Over?', we've been looking into how much we use technology, and what impact it's having on our lives.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
21 March 2016 Last updated at 16:44 GMT
We spoke to some 11-12 year olds to find out how much time they spend using their tablets, phones, computers and TV's every day.
The results showed that 71% of them used technology for more than 4 hours everyday, outside of school hours.
